summary: I don't think anyone could understand what Captain Marvel means to me. She's made up the best years of my life and tomorrow we...
body: I don’t think anyone could understand what Captain Marvel means to me. She’s made up the best years of my life and tomorrow we finally get a trailer for her movie! I never thought Marvel would give her an appearance within their MCU, and now here she is headlining her own title within a film! I remember crying when it was announced, crying when Brie was cast, crying when the concept art was released, crying looking at set photos and crying when the promo photos were released. I could not be more proud and happy to be a fan and tomorrow will be the turning point. Her time and our time is coming, Carol Corps! We stand together and we will make this a historic moment in Marvel!
